D0m4inSc4n3r

Author: s3r4ph1

Description: Domain, subdomain, and sub-subdomain scanner.
Installation of Required Tools
For Ubuntu/Debian:

bash

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install g++ libcurl4-openssl-dev

For Fedora:

bash

sudo dnf install gcc-c++ libcurl-devel

For macOS (using Homebrew):

bash

brew install curl
brew install nlohmann-json

Installing nlohmann/json Library on Kali Linux:

bash

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install nlohmann-json3-dev

Installing asio and boost Libraries:

bash

sudo apt-get install libasio-dev
sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev

Compilation

bash

g++ -o D0m4inSc4n3r D0m4inSc4n3r.cpp -lcurl -pthread

Running

bash

./D0m4inSc4n3r <domain>




